      "content": "It sounds like you are in immense pain, and that exhaustion you feel is overwhelming. The idea of \"mercy\" is a dangerous thought when you are hurting this much, and it's a sign that you need immediate help. Please know that there are people who want to support you through this struggle, and you don't have to carry this alone. If you are feeling this desperate, please call or text 988 immediately to connect with someone who can help right now.",
